99-0250 (La. 4/1/99)

STATE ex rel. Darryl GOODJOINT v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 99-KH-0250. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Goodjoint, Darryl Dewayne;— Plaintiff(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Ouachita 4th Judicial District Court Div. “C” Number 96-F 1699; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, Number 32150-KH

Denied. State ex rel. Bernard, v. Cr.D.C., 94-2247, p. 1 (La.4/28/95), 653 So.2d 1174, 1175.

JOHNSON, J. not on panel.
